## File Naming Convention
`13WCF-Activity Rollforward App v{MAJOR}.{MINOR}.py`

When updating:
1. Increment MINOR for bug fixes and small changes (1.0 → 1.1)
2. Increment MAJOR for significant features or breaking changes (1.9 → 2.0)
3. Archive old version to Archive/Old_Versions_{DATE}/
4. Update this VERSION file
5. Update START_PYTHON_APP.command with new filename
6. Commit changes to git with version tag
